Defendant Pablo D Beyer in court, in custody, with attorney Kelsey Loshaw.   Andrea M Will appeared for the State of Wisconsin.  State makes sentencing argument.  Defendant's brother, Jose B., makes statement.  Defense makes statement.  Defendant makes statement.  The Defendant was sentenced to the following:

COUNT 1:

IMPOSED SENTENCE of: 

6 YEARS IMPRISONMENT (CREDIT - 521 days)
  - 3 YEAR(S) OF INITIAL CONFINEMENT
  - 3 YEAR(S) OF EXTENDED SUPERVISION;

CONDITIONS OF EXTENDED SUPERVISION:  
*Follow through with any treatment and/or counseling recommended by Agent;
*Sex Offender Registry

COURT COSTS:  $268.00 (to be paid from prison wages and/or to be paid as a condition of extended supervision);

DNA SURCHARGE:  $250.00 (to be paid from prison wages and/or to be paid as a condition of extended supervision);
Defendant to provide DNA sample, if not yet provided, immediately if in custody otherwise within (3) business days at the Waukesha County Sheriff Department.

CHILD PORNOGRAPHY IMAGE SURCHARGE:  $5,000.00 (to be paid from prison wages and/or to be paid as a condition of extended supervision);

Defendant is eligible for Challenge Incarceration Program.
Defendant is not eligible for Substance Abuse Program.

Felony warnings, voting rights and firearms warnings given.
